events.text: The Pistons traded Andre Drummond, Deividas Sirvydis, and Luke Kennard to the Nuggets for Mason Plumlee and Will Barton.
The North Carolina traded James Johnson and Goran Dragic to the Thunder for Chris Paul and a 2021 2nd round pick (OKC).
The Hawks traded Cam Reddish to the North Carolina for Tyler Herro.
The Hawks traded DeAndre' Bembry to the Thunder for a 2020 1st round pick (DEN).
The Thunder traded Goran Dragic to the Mavericks for Courtney Lee, Jalen Brunson, Justin Jackson, and a 2020 2nd round pick (GSW).
The Thunder traded James Johnson to the Lakers for a 2023 2nd round pick (LAL).
The Lakers traded Talen Horton-Tucker, Kentavious Caldwell-Pope, and a 2020 1st round pick (LAL) to the Hornets for Willy Hernangomez and a 2020 2nd round pick (CLE).
The Thunder traded Danilo Gallinari, Courtney Lee, and a 2023 1st round pick (OKC) to the Spurs for LaMarcus Aldridge and Patty Mills.

The Thunder traded LaMarcus Aldridge and a 2020 2nd round pick (GSW) to the North Carolina for Justise Winslow, Dion Waiters, Bam Adebayo, a 2020 1st round pick (MIA), and a 2022 2nd round pick (MIA).

born.loc: Tuzla, Republic of Bosnia and Herzegovina
